{
  "stem": "14715.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then, a certain amount of people from our commando, they were taking them out one by one and putting them next to an elevator going up one floor.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And on top of the elevator, there was another commando taking them off the elevator and laying them out on the floor on the side of the ovens, four, five, the whole length in both sides where the ovens were.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And one man on either side went out with a pair of pliers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They used to call them the dentists.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they were pulling out the gold teeth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "This was going on day and night on a 12-hour base shifts.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The people who worked in those crematoriums was 12 hours.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then the ovens had to be cooled-- didn't even have a chance to cool off, the ashes were taken out, outside with wheelbarrows, steel wheelbarrows.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And there was another commando having in their hands stampers, it's a metal plate with a wooden stake-- and stamping the ashes and sifting them through a screen.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Then another commando was loading them on trucks and wagons.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they pulled them towards the river.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They dumped this in the river.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The river was [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Vistula, Tistula, something Polish-- Vistula River something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, a friend of mine who went back many years later brought some ashes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we have a memorial in Brandeis University.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we have little ashes on our own buried in that particular place which came from Vistula River.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know exactly how you spell it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If they were, maybe just a few got special-- some signias or bands that they can go in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because, otherwise, you wouldn't know who was who.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We wore civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
